'''保罗·戴维·伊佐''' （{{lang-en|'''Paul David Izzo'''}}，{{bd|1995年|1月6日}}，{{IPA-it|ˈpul ˈitsˈɔ}}），是一名[[澳洲|澳洲]]職業足球員，司職[[守門員_(足球)|守門員]]，現效力[[澳職|澳職]]球會[[中岸水手足球會|中岸水手]]。

==球會生涯==

===阿德萊德聯===
2012年12月1日，伊佐在對作客對[[中岸水手足球會|中岸水手]]首在上場，代替因為參加國家隊而無法出賽的[[尤金·加莱科维奇|尤金·加莱科维奇]]。他首次在主場上場是12月7日對[[墨尔本胜利足球俱乐部|墨爾本勝利]]的比賽<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/adelaideunited/players/Paul-Izzo/4924 | title = Paul Izzo | publisher = footballaustralia.com.au | accessdate = 18 July 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120930081543/http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/adelaideunited/players/Paul-Izzo/4924 | archivedate = 2012年9月30日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://aus.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/paul-izzo/ | title = Paul Izzo | publisher = worldfootball.net | accessdate = 18 July 2012 | archive-date = 2019-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191214033342/http://aus.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/paul-izzo/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/aleague/matchcentre/lineup/Adelaide-United-FC-v-Melbourne-Victory-FC-Hyundai-A-League/2659 | title = Adelaide United FC vs Melbourne Victory FC: Team lineup | publisher = footballaustralia.com.au | accessdate = 16 December 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204551/http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/aleague/matchcentre/lineup/Adelaide-United-FC-v-Melbourne-Victory-FC-Hyundai-A-League/2659 | archivedate = 2013年10月29日 }}</ref>。2013/14球季的[[澳洲足總盃|澳洲足總盃]]第一輪對[[威靈頓鳳凰足球俱樂部|威靈頓鳳凰]]的賽事，他被安排以先發身份上場，保持清白之身以1-0晉級。2014年12月31日作客威靈頓鳳凰的比賽，由於首席門將加莱科维奇需參加亞洲盃，使伊佐有上場機會，最終以3-0輸球<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/football/64583729/tyler-boyds-late-double-fires-wellington-phoenix-up-to-third-on-aleague-ladder | title = Tyler Boyd's late double fires Wellington Phoenix up to third on A-League ladder | publisher = stuff.co.nz | date = 1 January 2014 | accessdate = 10 July 2015 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161545/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/football/64583729/tyler-boyds-late-double-fires-wellington-phoenix-up-to-third-on-aleague-ladder | dead-url = no }}</ref>。之後他在對[[珀斯光輝|珀斯光輝]]和[[紐卡素噴射機|紐卡素噴射機]]的比賽上場，均取得勝利。

===中岸水手===
伊佐在2015年7月8日被球會放棄，之後立即與另一澳職球會中岸水手簽約兩年加盟<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ccmariners.com.au/article/news-izzo-inks-with-mariners/vp1hv3g3tsax17dacggwr8luu|publisher={{ALeague CCM}}|title=Izzo inks with Mariners|date=8 July 2015|accessdate=8 July 2015|archive-date=2017-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902013820/http://www.ccmariners.com.au/article/news-izzo-inks-with-mariners/vp1hv3g3tsax17dacggwr8luu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
伊佐曾代表[[澳洲20歲以下國家足球隊|澳洲U20]]出戰在[[阿聯酋|阿聯酋]]舉行的[[2012年亞足聯U19青年錦標賽|2012年亞足聯U19青年錦標賽]]。

